result.title: MBSTU Practice Contest 1
result.content:
There will be a individual contest with respect to upcoming ICPC. The contest link will be found here at 9.55PM at 21-October-2014.

How to participate in the contest.

  1. You will find the contest link under the contest tab.
  2. At 9.55 register for the contest by clicking virtual participation.
  3. After five mins the contest will start and you can see and solve the problem. The Contest will be regular Codeforces mode.

Many thnx to Bidhan vai for setting this contest fo us.

Good Luck and Happy Coding.
